snippet.title: Dungeon Keeper 2 - Video Game Trailer (1998, Windows)
snippet.description:
Dungeon Keeper 2 -  Trailer
Developped by Bullfrog Productions.
Published by Electronic Arts for PC Windows in 1999.
Trailer announced also a release for Playstation, but this version was cancelled.

Video found on Dungeon Keeper Gold game disc (1998)
